PIC GLCD Library

Welcome to the GLCD Library for PIC. It is a derivate of the original Arduino KS0108 Library. 
It has been ported to PIC by Ivan de Jesus Deras (ideras@gmail.com). This port is based on version 2
of that Library.

You can find the original library at 

http://www.arduino.cc/playground/Code/GLCDks0108

Tested only on PIC16F887 !